      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>__Propagators__</para>

          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>RKV89PointMass</para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>

      +~hs~~hs~~hs~This propagator simply sets the Earth as a point mass and uses it as the Force Model. All other propagators below, except for one (RKV8912x12), use Earth as a point mass as well. Figure below shows this propagator properties' window; windows for other propagators will look similarly. 

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Rename DefaultProp to RKV89PointMass</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Set the Initial Step Size to 30</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Set the Accuracy at 1e-012</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Set the Min Step Size to 30</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Set the Max Step Size to 30</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Set the Degree in the Gravity Group box to 0</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Set the Order in the Gravity Group box to 0</para>

          <para>{img src=show_image.php?name=FMrkv89pointmass.jpg
          align="center"}</para>

          <para>
            <screenshot>
              <info>
                <title />
              </info>

              <mediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                  <imagedata align="center" fileref="???" />
                </imageobject>

                <caption>
                  <para />
                </caption>
              </mediaobject>
            </screenshot>
          </para>

          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>RKV89ThirdBodies</para>

              <para>+~hs~~hs~~hs~This propagator adds all the planets except
              Mercury and Pluto as point masses to the Force Model.</para>

              <itemizedlist>
                <listitem>
                  <para>Add a Propagator and rename it RKV89ThirdBodies</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Set the Initial Step Size to 30</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Set the Accuracy at 1e-012</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Set the Min Step Size to 30</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Set the Max Step Size to 30 as well</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Set the Degree in the Gravity Group box to 0</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Set the Order in the Gravity Group box to 0</para>
                </listitem>

                <listitem>
                  <para>Add Sun, Luna, and all the planets except Mercury and
                  Pluto to the Point Masses field</para>

                  <itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                      <para>RKV8912x12</para>

                      <para>+~hs~~hs~~hs~Unlike other propagators, this one
                      does not set Earth as a point mass in the Force Model;
                      it uses instead a 12x12 JGM-2 Gravity Model.</para>

                      <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                          <para>Add a Propagator and rename it
                          RKV8912x12</para>
                        </listitem>

                        <listitem>
                          <para>Set the Initial Step Size to 30</para>
                        </listitem>

                        <listitem>
                          <para>Set the Accuracy at 1e-012</para>
                        </listitem>

                        <listitem>
                          <para>Set the Min Step Size to 30</para>
                        </listitem>

                        <listitem>
                          <para>Set the Max Step Size to 30 as well</para>
                        </listitem>

                        <listitem>
                          <para>Raise the Degree in the Gravity Group box to
                          12</para>
                        </listitem>

                        <listitem>
                          <para>Raise the Order in the Gravity Group box to
                          12</para>

                          <itemizedlist>
                            <listitem>
                              <para>RKV89MSISE90</para>

                              <para>+~hs~~hs~~hs~The Force Model in this
                              Propagator calculates drag on the spacecraft based
                              on the MSISE90 Atmospheric Model.</para>

                              <itemizedlist>
                                <listitem>
                                  <para>Add a Propagator and rename it
                                  RKV89MSISE90</para>
                                </listitem>

                                <listitem>
                                  <para>Set the Accuracy at 1e-012</para>
                                </listitem>

                                <listitem>
                                  <para>Set the Min Step Size to 30</para>
                                </listitem>

                                <listitem>
                                  <para>Set the Max Step Size to 30 as well</para>
                                </listitem>

                                <listitem>
                                  <para>Lower the Degree in the Gravity Group box to
                                  0</para>
                                </listitem>

                                <listitem>
                                  <para>Lower the Order in the Gravity Group box down
                                  to 0</para>
                                </listitem>

                                <listitem>
                                  <para>Set the Atmosphere Model under the Drag Group
                                  Box to MSISE90</para>

                                  <itemizedlist>
                                    <listitem>
                                      <para>RKV89JR</para>

                                      <para>+~hs~~hs~~hs~The Force Model in this
                                      Propagator calculates drag on the spacecraft based
                                      on the Jacchia-Roberts Atmosphere Model.</para>

                                      <itemizedlist>
                                        <listitem>
                                          <para>Add a Propagator and rename it RKV89JR</para>
                                        </listitem>

                                        <listitem>
                                          <para>Set the Initial Step Size to 30</para>
                                        </listitem>

                                        <listitem>
                                          <para>Set the Accuracy at 1e-012</para>
                                        </listitem>

                                        <listitem>
                                          <para>Set the Min Step Size to 30</para>
                                        </listitem>

                                        <listitem>
                                          <para>Set the Max Step Size to 30 as well</para>
                                        </listitem>

                                        <listitem>
                                          <para>Lower the Degree in the Gravity Group box to
                                          0</para>
                                        </listitem>

                                        <listitem>
                                          <para>Lower the Order in the Gravity Group box down
                                          to 0</para>
                                        </listitem>

                                        <listitem>
                                          <para>Set the Atmosphere Model under the Drag Group
                                          Box to JacchiaRoberts</para>

                                          <itemizedlist>
                                            <listitem>
                                              <para>RKV89SRP</para>

                                              <para>+~hs~~hs~~hs~This propagator is like the first
                                              one (RKV89PointMass), with the only difference that
                                              it accounts for the Solar Radiation Pressure.</para>

                                              <itemizedlist>
                                                <listitem>
                                                  <para>Add a Propagator and rename it RKV89SRP</para>
                                                </listitem>

                                                <listitem>
                                                  <para>Set the Initial Step Size to 30</para>
                                                </listitem>

                                                <listitem>
                                                  <para>Set the Accuracy at 1e-012</para>
                                                </listitem>

                                                <listitem>
                                                  <para>Set the Min Step Size to 30</para>
                                                </listitem>

                                                <listitem>
                                                  <para>Set the Max Step Size to 30 as well</para>
                                                </listitem>

                                                <listitem>
                                                  <para>Lower the Degree in the Gravity Group box to
                                                  0</para>
                                                </listitem>

                                                <listitem>
                                                  <para>Lower the Order in the Gravity Group box down
                                                  to 0</para>
                                                </listitem>

                                                <listitem>
                                                  <para>Check the Use Solar Radiation Pressure Check
                                                  box</para>

                                                  <itemizedlist>
                                                    <listitem>
                                                      <para>__Burns__</para>

